+/*
+ *  call-seq:
+ *     RubyVM::Frame.new(thread)          -> frame_object
+ *
+ *  Returns an RubyVM::Frame object which can contains dynamic frame
+ *  information. Don't use this directly. Instead use one of the 
+ *  class methods.
